  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00405', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-099-ba81c82b', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-04', NULL, 'essay', '設市地開發者只採用土地和資本兩種生產要素，興建不同樓層的建築物。茲暫不考慮
