定？又於建物造價上漲時，此等最適組合將產生何種變化？試繪圖說明之。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "04a8c8f14941", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099150", "c": "905", "s": "600", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "不動產經濟學", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年律師、會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL),
