定基準、土地使用強度等規範由相關主管機關商定之。你對該規定的見解為何？試
從規劃管制的觀點予以論述之。（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "04a8c8f14941", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099150", "c": "905", "s": "600", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "不動產經濟學", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年律師、會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": "四", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00408', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-099-9a386a01', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '「木末芙蓉花，山中發紅萼。澗戶寂無人，紛紛開且落。」（王維〈辛夷塢〉）下列成語，何者可以詮 釋此詩意境？', '["出水芙蓉", "一枝獨秀", "空谷幽蘭", "名花傾國"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aa2715d75041", "answer_pdf_sha1": "54154d8d65c4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099150", "c": "905", "s": "200", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文（作文與測驗）", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年律師、會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00409', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-099-9a386a01', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關信封受信人的寫法，下列何者為錯誤的選項？', '["張學富主任  鈞啟", "張主任學富  鈞啟", "張學富  主任（右偏）  鈞啟", "張主任  學富（右偏）  鈞啟"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aa2715d75041", "answer_pdf_sha1": "54154d8d65c4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099150", "c": "905", "s": "200", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文（作文與測驗）", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年律師、會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00410', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-099-9a386a01', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '「王子犯法，與庶民同罪」，不論古今，人們對政令法律要求的都是期待上下一律的公正公平，下列敘 述並不包含此種精神的選項是：', '["法不阿貴；繩不撓曲（《韓非子．有度》）", "誅不避貴，賞不遺賤（《晏子春秋．內篇問上》）", "厲法禁，自大臣始，則小臣不犯矣（蘇軾《策刑第六》）", "明刑而不濫乎所恨，審賞而不加乎附己（葛洪《抱朴子．臣節》）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aa2715d75041", "answer_pdf_sha1": "54154d8d65c4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099150", "c": "905", "s": "200", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文（作文與測驗）", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年律師、會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00411', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-099-9a386a01', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '子曰：「富而可求也，雖執鞭之士，吾亦為之；如不可求，從吾所好。」（《論語．述而》）下列闡釋 最切合上文主旨的選項是：', '["追求財富，須謹守原則", "貧富貴賤，原各有命定", "執鞭之士，有致富之日", "鐘鼎山林，應相互尊重"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aa2715d75041", "answer_pdf_sha1": "54154d8d65c4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099150", "c": "905", "s": "200", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文（作文與測驗）", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年律師、會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00412', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-099-9a386a01', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '語言文字的使用往往會影響讀者的觀感和判斷，以美國對婦女墮胎事件的爭議為例，支持墮胎者主張 「選擇的權利」，反對者則高呼「生存的權利」，對同一事件雙方說法迥然不同，最主要是因為下列何 種原因：', '["支持者只考慮人權的問題，反對者則只顧及道德人性", "支持者使用的語言太激進，反對者使用的語言比較保守", "支持者的主張是從婦女的立場而言，而反對者的主張則從嬰兒的立場出發", "「選擇」和「生存」兩詞語意正好相反對立，正反雙方藉以表達不同立場"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:06+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "aa2715d75041", "answer_pdf_sha1": "54154d8d65c4", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "099150", "c": "905", "s": "200", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文（作文與測驗）", "year": "099", "exam_name": "099年律師、會計師、不動產估價師、專利師、民間之公證人、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing"], "slug": "appraiser", "db_exam_id": "real-estate-appraiser"}'::jsonb, NULL)
